It&#39;s accidentally RESTful for &quot;get me this data&quot; operations that
happen to use GET, and for mutating operations that happen to use
POST.  But the clients would be unnecessarily tightly coupled to
servers, and it otherwise doesn&#39;t seem to help with
resource-orientation.

http://www.markbaker.ca/blog/2005/04/14/accidentally-restful/

